Class Activity

java.lang.Object
Activity
public class Activity extends Object
The Activity class represents an activity that can be booked by passengers. Each activity has a unique code, name, description, destination, cost, capacity, current bookings, and a list of enrolled passengers.

    • Activity

      public Activity()
      Constructs an Activity object with default values. Default values: act_code = -1, act_name = "NA", act_destination = "NA", act_description = "NA", Cost = -1, capacity = -1, bookings = 0. The list of enrolled_passengers is initialized as an empty ArrayList.
